importing:
----------

    >>> try:
    ...     import unittest2 as unittest
    ... except ImportError:
    ...     import unittest

test case:
----------
    >>> class SomeTestCase(unittest.TestCase):
    ...     def setUp(self):
    ...         pass

    ...     def tearDown(self):
    ...         pass

failing a test
--------------

    >>> def some_failing_test(self):
    ...     self.fail()

